TextEng: Who are you?
Who am you?
What happened here?
What happen here?
Farewell.
Me go now.
You burned down your own home?
You burn own home? You stupid?
Is there anything I can do for you?
Me do anything for yous?
That's tough luck, all right.
Oh well. That too bad, me guess.
So you have absolutely nothing left at all?
Text: 그래서 정말 아무것도 남은 게 없다는 거야?

TextEng: So yous gots nothing left at all? Nothings?
Text: 그래서 진짜 아무것도 안 남았어? 아무것도?

TextEng: Ah-HA! If you can buy a shirt, you've got gold! Give it to me!
Text: 아하! 셔츠를 살 수 있다면 금화가 있다는 거잖아! 나한테 내놔!

TextEng: Ah-HA! So you gots gold to buy shirts! You gives it to me!
Text: 아하! 셔츠 살 금화 있잖아! 나한테 내놔!

TextEng: I won't kill you. I'll say you killed your family. You'll rot in prison for their murders!
Text: 죽이지 않을게. 대신 네가 네 가족을 죽였다고 말하겠어. 살인죄로 감옥에서 썩게 될 거야!

TextEng: Me not kill you. Me just say you killed you's family. You gonna rot in jail for murders!
Text: 나 너 안 죽여. 대신 너가 네 가족 죽였다고 말할 거야. 너 살인으로 감옥에서 썩을 거야!

TextEng: I'm sorry. I lost my head for a moment. I apologize.
Me sorry, me gots crazy for a bit. Me sorry.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 잠깐 미쳤었어. 나 미안해.
